description:
Laurie Voss analyzes the state of the Jamstack based on an industry survey of 3,000 developers. According to survey responses, the most sought-after benefits of the Jamstack are performance, reliability and developer workflows, while one third of respondents reported their Jamstack sites serve millions of users each year.

Read more https://www.netlify.com/blog/2020/05/27/state-of-the-jamstack-survey-2020-first-results/
